 provide further powerful tools and\nmethods to study the problem of detecting vehicles at night before they are\nactually visible.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 25 Apr 2022 09:56:34 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 27 Sep 2022 09:13:36 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-09-28"}
