f the plant and can be\ncharacterised by the model parameters. Considering a scenario of high\ngreenhouse emissions, our model forecasts that {\\it Posidonia oceanica} meadows\nwill lose 70$\\%$ of their population by the year $2050$. {\\it Cymodocea\nnodosa}, with higher thermal resilience, acts as an opportunistic species\nconquering the space left by the degraded {\\it Posidonia oceanica}.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 25 Apr 2022 11:09:59 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 29 Apr 2022 15:25:31 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 11 May 2023 16:42:34 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-05-12"}
