a fleet of 5,000 EVs would result in the equivalent $\\textrm{CO}_2$\nof removing one Combined Cycle Gas Turbine from the system. This significant\nincrease in revenue and carbon savings show this approach is worth\ninvestigating for potential future application.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 25 Apr 2022 11:21:32 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-05-12"}
